article_title: Texas Officer Resigns After Pool-Party Video
article_text:
The police officer who was caught on video wrestling a 14-year-old girl to the ground at a pool party in a Dallas suburb last week resigned from the city’s police department Tuesday.

Cpl. David Eric Casebolt’s actions “as seen on the video of the disturbance at the community pool, are indefensible,” said McKinney Police Chief Greg Conley during a news conference. “Our policies, our training and our practices do not support his...
